long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Earth View 360° new tab features Earth & Satellite Image Search, Web Search, Custom Backgrounds, Weather, Shortcuts & Date/Time.

The Installation of this extension will configure your New Tab Page to Earth View 360°. Earth View 360° extension is all you need to start browsing with quick access to earth maps & web search.

Permissions we request:

New Tab:
This permission allows the extension to replace the page you see when opening a new tab

Privacy Policy: https://earthview360.org/privacy.html
EULA: https://earthview360.org/eula.html

Uninstall Instructions: 
https://earthview360.org/uninstall.html
